import React from 'react'
import { Box, Typography } from '@mui/material'


const Register: React.FC = () => {
    return (
      <Box sx={{
        background: '#1E1E1E', 
        minHeight: '100vh', 
        display: 'flex',
        flexDirection: 'column',
        justifyContent: 'center',
        alignItems: 'center',
      }}>
        <Box sx={{ background: '#332F2F', width: '300px', height: '550px', borderRadius: '20px' }}>
          <Box sx={{ background: '#332F2F', width: '300px', height: '150px', borderTopLeftRadius: '20px', borderTopRightRadius: '20px' }}>
            <Typography sx={{ fontSize: '48px' }}>Atlas End√©mico</Typography>
          </Box>
          <Box sx={{ background: '#ffffff', width: '300px', height: '400px', borderRadius: '20px', borderTopLeftRadius: '100px', borderTopRightRadius: '0px' }}>
            <Typography sx={{ color: '#000000', fontSize: '32px' }} pt={2}>Cadastro</Typography>
          </Box>
        </Box>
      </Box>
    )
}

export default Register
